      <title>Refureku</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/refureku/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/refureku/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solo project&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech stack:&lt;/strong&gt; C++17, libclang, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ToruNiina/toml11&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;toml11&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;, Visual Studio 2019, Git, Trello&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Target platforms :&lt;/strong&gt; Windows / Linux / MacOS&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/jsoysouvanh/Refureku&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;Refureku&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt; is a C++17 dynamic reflection library I wrote as a personnal project in my free time. The github repository has a (hopefully nice) README highlighting the library main functionalities, as well as a &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/jsoysouvanh/Refureku/wiki&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xD;&#xA;  class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xD;&#xA;&gt;full wiki&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;svg id=&#34;external-link&#34; class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt; going into more details. There&amp;rsquo;s not much to write here, just check the repository out ;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
